### State Management

- **Zustand** — client/ephemeral state: auth token, execution progress, UI state
- **TanStack React Query** — server state: projects, features, test cases (fetched + cached)
- **SSE** — streaming AI progress events (context build, test generation, execution) via native `fetch`

**Zustand stores summary:**

| Store | File | Persisted | Purpose |
|-------|------|-----------|---------|
| `useAuthStore` | `authStore.ts` | ✅ localStorage | JWT token, user, `skipped` flag. `clearAuth()` resets all. |
| `useKeyStore` | `keyStore.ts` | ❌ memory only | Anthropic key in-memory for session. Hydrated from OS keychain via IPC on load. |
| `useAppStore` | `useAppStore.ts` | ❌ | Active sidebar section |
| `testSuiteExecutionStore` | `testSuiteExecutionStore.ts` | ❌ | Live test run state — tests, activity log, pause/abort/guidance state |
| `executionStore` | `executionStore.ts` | ❌ | Legacy free-form CU execution state (not used in main product flows) |

