## Human Click Pattern (Critical)

Never use instant clicks — always simulate human timing:

```python
pyautogui.moveTo(x, y, duration=0.2)
pyautogui.mouseDown()
time.sleep(0.1)   # debounce
pyautogui.mouseUp()
```

